name: Flying
description: This cat flies over people, finding the perfect moment to attack!.

name: Sleepy
description: The master of catnaps - can fall asleep anywhere at any time.

name: Zoomer
description: With the speed of light, this cat zooms around the house, leaving chaos in its wake.

name: Chatterbox
description: Constantly talking in cat language, providing commentary on everything.

name: Ninja
description: Master of stealth and agility, this cat can sneak up on you without a sound.

name: Yoga Guru
description: Practicing cat yoga poses with unmatched flexibility and zen vibes.

name: Foodie
description: Always on the lookout for the next delicious meal, this cat is a true gourmet.

name: Drama Queen
description: Dramatic reactions to everything, turning everyday events into soap opera scenes.

name: Explorer
description: Curiosity knows no bounds for this adventurous cat, always discovering new places.

name: Smarty Pants
description: A cat genius solving complex puzzles and outsmarting everyone.
